{"tid":1198760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當差當得耐會唔會中路法西效應，搞到殺紅了眼？","createTime":"2019-06-10T10:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T17:13:53.000Z","uid":249885,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"80ef996fd29d6ff2b5448be3b82e709c176a8eec","tid":1198760,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:16:48.000Z","msg":"路西法效應是指在特定情境或氛圍下，思維方式、行為方式、人的性格，表現出了惡的一面，這體現了人性中的「惡」是可以人為在特定情境下，或是直接由情境造成的。<br />\n<br />\n1.首先，在有意或不經意之情形下跨越自己的道德底線。<br />\n<br />\n2.將其他人或個體去人性化。<br />\n<br />\n3.將自己去識別化。(透過匿名、變裝等方式、如：三K黨)<br />\n<br />\n4.分散與推諉個人之責任。(如：納粹)<br />\n<br />\n5.盲目服從於權威。<br />\n<br />\n6.不經批判地盲目服從團體規範。<br />\n<br />\n7.藉由不作為與冷漠，被動地容忍惡存在。"},{"pid":"9de3a7ae72038f576cffdc59f757ed5f15b73a48","tid":1198760,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:31:07.000Z","msg":"黃之峰&amp;學民仔女<br />\n曾經打破特區警察既「第一扇窗」（佔領公民廣場）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n引發「破窗效應」而引發之後既 佔領馬路行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5d52597e240b89c0c8588023c7ea2458c3070c","tid":1198760,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}